snippet.title: BOMBFEST - Hand in Hand | PC and Consoles | NA
snippet.description:
BOMBFEST is explosive party-game fun for up to four players! Blow your enemies away and be the last toy standing, but don't get caught in a chain reaction of explosions! Buy it today on Playstation 4! Follow us at www.playbombfest.com

BOMBFEST: @playbombfest www.playbombfest.com
Whitethorn Digital: @whitethorngames www.whitethorndigital.com
